VaultPauseStatus(address,bool).notice: Emitted when a vault's status is updated

depositVaultCashToStrategyTokens(uint256.notice: Strategy vaults can call this method to deposit asset cash into strategy tokens.

params.assetCashToDepositExternal: the number of asset cash tokens to deposit (external)
params.maturity: the maturity of the vault where the redemption will take place
params.vaultData: arbitrary data to pass back to the vault for deposit

redeemStrategyTokensToCash(uint256,uint2.notice: Strategy vaults can call this method to redeem strategy tokens to cash and hold them as asset cash within the pool. This should typically be used during settlement but can also be used for vault-wide deleveraging.

params.maturity: the maturity of the vault where the redemption will take place
params.strategyTokensToRedeem: the number of strategy tokens redeemed
params.vaultData: arbitrary data to pass back to the vault

returns.assetCashRequiredToSettle: amount of asset cash still remaining to settle the debt
returns.underlyingCashRequiredToSettle: amount of underlying cash still remaining to settle the debt

reduceMaxBorrowCapacity(address,uint80,u.notice: Allows the owner to reduce the max borrow capacity on the vault and force the redemption of strategy tokens to cash to reduce the overall risk of the vault. This method is intended to be used in emergencies to mitigate insolvency risk.

params.maturity: the maturity to redeem tokens in, will generally be either the current maturity or the next maturity.
params.maxVaultBorrowCapacity: the new max vault borrow capacity
params.strategyTokensToRedeem: how many tokens we would want to redeem in the maturity
params.vaultData: vault data to pass to the vault

setVaultPauseStatus(address,bool).notice: Enables or disables a vault. If a vault is disabled, no one can enter the vault anymore.

params.enable: bool if the vault should be enabled immediately

settleVault(address,uint256,address[],ui.notice: Settles an entire vault, can only be called during an emergency stop out or during the vault's defined settlement period. May be called multiple times during a vault term if the vault has been stopped out early.

params.redeemCallData: call data passed to redeem for all accounts being settled
params.settleAccounts: a list of accounts to manually settle (if any)
params.vaultSharesToRedeem: the amount of vault shares to settle on each account
